## SECTION 2 — ACRONYM & TERM DICTIONARY

### Core Platform Acronyms

| Acronym | Full Name | Definition |
|---|---|---|
| **CRS** | Central Reservation System | The SynXis core hospitality reservation platform |
| **HSS** | Hospitality Service Suite | Enterprise WCF/.NET services layer (ProductManager, ProfileManager, etc.) |
| **ARI** | Availability, Rates, Inventory | The ARI integration service domain handling inventory/rate sync to channels |
| **OXI** | OPERA eXchange Interface | Oracle's PMS integration protocol used by Property Connect |
| **PMS** | Property Management System | Hotel-level system (OPERA is most common) |
| **PRC** | Property Connect | Umbrella integration service between SynXis CR and PMS (OPERA/OXI) |
| **CHC** | Channel Connect | Integration service for OTA/channel distribution (Expedia, Booking.com, etc.) |
| **GDS** | Global Distribution System | Travel agency systems (Sabre, Travelport, Amadeus) |
| **SDX** | Sabre Direct Connect | Sabre GDS direct connect integration |
| **TDX** | Travelport Direct Connect | Travelport GDS direct connect integration |
| **SBE** | Sabre Booking Engine | Consumer-facing booking application (ReactJS) |
| **SVA** | SynXis Voice Agent | Voice/call center booking channel |
| **GC** | Guest Connect | Mobile/web guest-facing booking interface |
| **CC** | Control Center | Property management UI (ASP.NET) |
| **RTAV** | Real-Time Availability | OXI message type: Physical Rooms, OOO, Definite Count, Tentative Count, Overbook |
| **ICE** | — | Modern REST API for reservations (Frontman layer) |
| **OTA** | Online Travel Agency | Third-party booking channels (Expedia, Booking.com, etc.) |
| **LOS** | Length of Stay | Number of nights for a reservation |
| **CTA** | Closed to Arrival | Stay restriction: no new arrivals on a date |
| **CTD** | Closed to Departure | Stay restriction: no departures on a date |
| **OOO** | Out of Order | Rooms removed from inventory (maintenance) |
| **OHIP** | Oracle Hospitality Integration Platform | Modern Oracle PMS integration protocol |
| **HTNG** | Hospitality Technology Next Generation | Industry standard for PMS integration |
| **BAR** | Best Available Rate | Dynamic best publicly available rate |
| **RevPAR** | Revenue Per Available Room | KPI: Total Revenue / Total Available Rooms |
| **CPD** | — | Central Payment Domain / Payment Processing |
| **HSPD** | Hospitality Product (Rally Project) | The Rally/Agile project workspace for SHS |
| **SON** | Specification of Need | Business requirements documents (product owner stories) |

### Infrastructure / Config Acronyms

| Acronym | Context | Meaning |
|---|---|---|
| `SVCARIPRC1` / `SVCARIPRC2` | connector.xml `User Id` | ARI database service account for Property Connect env 1/2 |
| `SVCARIPRC` | DB credentials | Pattern: SVC (Service Account) + ARI + PRC (Property Connect) |
| `TPRCDR` | interfaceconfiginfo.xml `pegasusAmenityCode` | Pegasus amenity code for Property Connect |
| `SAID Card` | Cloud infra | Service Asset and Integration Design card (YAML-based deployment descriptor) |
| `DomainQueueDirectorWindowsService` | Windows Service | Routes domain events via message queues |
| `IntegLogService` | Windows Service | Integration logging service |
| `InterfaceLoaderQReaderWindowsService` | Windows Service | Queue reader for interface loader |

