## SECTION 4 — ARCHITECTURE & INTEGRATION FLOWS

### Reservation Flow

```
Booking Channels (SBE / SVA / GC / OTA / GDS)
    ↓
SynXis CR (Central Reservation System)
    ├── HSS Services (Reservation, Rates, Inventory)
    ├── Property Connect (PRC) → OPERA PMS via OXI
    ├── Channel Connect (CHC) → OTA Channels
    └── ARI → Channel Inventory/Rate sync
```

### Property Connect (PRC) Bidirectional Flow

```
OUTBOUND: SynXis CR → Property Connect → OPERA PMS
  - Reservation Delivery (create/modify/cancel)
  - Content Push (rates, packages, configuration)
  - Group delivery

INBOUND: OPERA PMS/ORS → Property Connect → SynXis CR
  - RTAV (Real-Time Availability update)
    Fields: Physical Rooms, Out of Order, Definite Count,
            Tentative Count, House Overbook, Room Type Overbook
```

### ARI Flow

```
SynXis CR (Inventory/Rate changes)
    → ARI Processor
    → ARI Push Service
    → Channel Connect / OTA channels
    (also feeds: ARI API, ARI DTO Builder, ARI Shopping Service)
```

